description: - PUBLIC fieldSet returns: ID and profile object (status, privacyStatus and activityStatus will return with UNKNOWN values).
- FULL field_set returns: ID, status, contact and profile objects, privacy_status, activity_status, created_date, and updated_date.

docs.summary: Makes current logged in member not part of the community.
description: After this action, logged in member will not be able to be social in page.
For example: member will not be visible in all members page and site visitors, other members will not be able to see his/her profile
Returns full member entity with updated privacy_status.

docs.summary: Makes currently logged in member part of the community.
description: After this action, logged in member will be able to be social in page.
For example: member will be visible in all members page and site visitors, other members will be able to see his/her profile
Returns full member entity with updated privacy_status.

members.name: profilePhoto
members.doc:
Photo picture, which is used as a profile picture.

Fields `photo.offset_x` and `photo.offset_y` are **not** respected.

members.name: coverPhoto
members.doc:
Photo picture, which is used as a profile picture.

Fields `photo.offset_x` and `photo.offset_y` are **not** respected.

members.name: status
members.doc:
Member site access status. There are 5 options:

- OFFLINE: Member cannot login to the site.
- BLOCKED: Member cannot login to the site.
- APPROVED: Member can login to the site.
- PENDING: Member created and is waiting for approval by site owner.
- UNKNOWN: Caller has no permission or not requested to read this value.
One of:
 + `"UNKNOWN"`
 + `"PENDING"`
 + `"APPROVED"`
 + `"BLOCKED"`
 + `"OFFLINE"`

members.name: privacyStatus
members.doc:
Member privacy status. There are 3 options:

- PUBLIC: Member is visible to the site visitors, other site members, owners and apps.
- PRIVATE: Member becomes hidden to the site visitors and other site members. Member is returned only to site owners and apps with MEMBERS.MEMBER_READ_PRIVATE permission.
- UNKNOWN: Caller has no permission or has not requested to read this value.
One of:
 + `"UNKNOWN"`
 + `"PRIVATE"`
 + `"PUBLIC"`

members.name: activityStatus
members.doc:
Member activity status. There are 3 options:

- ACTIVE: This member can post in the forum and add comments in the blog.
- MUTED: This member can't post in the forum or add comments in the blog.
- UNKNOWN: The caller has no permission or has not requested to read this value.
One of:
 + `"UNKNOWN"`
 + `"ACTIVE"`
 + `"MUTED"`
